%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20marked%20improvement.%20There%20was%20only%20Patanjali%20earlier%2C%20now%20there%20are%20names.%20We%20appreciate%20that.%20They%20have%20understood%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanulla%20said%20after%20examining%20the%20public%20apology%20issued%20by%20Patanjali%20Ayurved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20asked%20Ramdev%20and%20Acharya%20Balkrishna%20to%20file%20on%20record%20the%20original%20page%20of%20each%20newspaper%20in%20which%20public%20apology%20was%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20took%20stern%20exception%20to%20comments%20made%20by%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20President%20RV%20Asokan%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20were%20flagged%20by%20Senior%20Advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20who%20represented%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20asked%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20to%20bring%20the%20IMA%20Director's%20interview%20with%20PTI%20on%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBring%20it%20on%20record.%20This%20will%20be%20more%20serious%20than%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20till%20now.%20Be%20prepared%20for%20more%20serious%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Amanullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20not%20covered%20yourself%20with%20glory%20and%20how%20can%20you%20decide%20what%20the%20court%20will%20do%2C%20if%20this%20is%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20IMA's%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMA%20President%20had%20told%20the%20PTI%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20criticised%20the%20IMA%20and%20the%20practices%20of%20private%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20sincerely%20believe%20they%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20was%20the%20material%20before%20them.%20They%20perhaps%20did%20not%20consider%20that%20this%20was%20not%20the%20issue%20that%20was%20before%20them%20in%20the%20court.%20It%20does%20not%20behove%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20a%20broadside%20against%20the%20medical%20profession%20of%20the%20country%20which%20after%20all%20sacrificed%20so%20many%20lives%20for%20the%20Covid%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20V%20Asokan%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Asokan%20was%20replying%20to%20a%20query%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observation%20in%20its%20hearing%20on%20April%2023%20that%20when%20it%20was%20pointing%20one%20finger%20at%20Patanjali%2C%20the%20remaining%20four%20fingers%20were%20pointed%20towards%20IMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20Uttarakhand%20State%20Licensing%20Authority%20for%20inaction%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20dissatisfaction%20over%20the%20explanation%20offered%20by%20the%20body%2C%20the%20top%20court%20observed%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20licensing%20authority%20took%20action%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20only%20after%20the%20apex%20court's%20April%2010%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2010%2C%20the%20court%20tore%20into%20the%20Uttarakhand%20licensing%20authority%20for%20not%20acting%20against%20Patanjali%20for%20so%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20directed%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20to%20stop%20all%20electronic%20and%20print%20advertisements%20of%20its%20medicines%20giving%20misleading%26quot%3B%20information%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20began%20in%20November%20last%20year%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20IMA%2C%20cautioned%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20against%20making%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20claims%20in%20advertisements%20about%20its%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMA%20had%20referred%20to%20several%20advertisements%20which%20allegedly%20projected%20the%20allopathy%20and%20the%20doctors%20in%20poor%20light%2C%20sayin