as%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20social%20media%20which%20sees%20him%20play%20'Pehle%20Bhi%20Main'%20while%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20enjoys%20it.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20video%20is%20recorded%20by%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20who%20he%20thanked%20for%20such%20a%20wonderful%20moment!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Woman%20Contracts%20Life-Threatening%20Bacteria%20After%20Dream%20Vacation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E18-year-old%20Claudia%20Gill's%20dream%20vacation%20turned%20into%20a%20fight%20for%20survival.%20After%20returning%20home%20from%20Queensland%2C%20Claudia%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20brutal%20combination%20of%20fatigue%2C%20excruciating%20ear%20sensitivity%2C%20and%20a%20constant%20ringing%20in%20her%20ears.%20Soon%2C%20a%20stiff%20neck%2C%20vomiting%2C%20and%20fainting%20sent%20her%20rushing%20to%20the%20hospital.%20There%2C%20doctors%20delivered%20a%20chilling%20diagnosis%20-%20meningococcus%20B%2C%20a%20potentially%20fatal%20bacterial%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20close%20call%20with%20death%20left%20Ms%20Gill%20hospitalized%20for%20five%20nights%2C%20followed%20by%20weeks%20of%20recovery%20and%20a%20gradual%20return%20to%20studies.%20Even%20two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20battles%20more%20frequent%20and%20severe%20headaches.%20Ms%20Gill's%20brush%20with%20mortality%20has%20fueled%20her%20desire%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20meningococcal%20symptoms%2C%20hoping%20to%20prevent%20others%20from%20facing%20the%20same%20terrifying%20ordeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gill%20connected%20with%20community%20and%20advocacy%20groups%20and%20realised%20she%20would%20be%20a%20good%20test%20case%20for%20education%20about%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20so%20quickly%2C%20it%20was%20pretty%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gill%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2