%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20with%20six%20separate%20ideas%20before%20moving%20forward%20with%20HelloData.ai.%20Marc%20kept%20in%20touch%20with%20us%20and%20decided%20to%20join%20our%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaving%20a%20stable%20job%20and%20cofounding%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FHelloData.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelloData.ai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20wasn't%20a%20quick%20decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeciding%20to%20leave%20my%20stable%20job%20took%20a%20year%20of%20wrestling%20with%20questions%2C%20especially%20from%20my%20family.%20Security%2C%20prestige%2C%20and%20a%20steady%20paycheck%20%E2%80%94%20why%20trade%20those%20for%20the%20unknowns%20of%20a%20startup%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20one%20answer%2C%20but%20I%20had%20several%20realizations%20I%20couldn't%20ignore.%20First%2C%20I%20craved%20the%20startup%20energy.%20The%20constant%20challenges%20and%20rush%20of%20innovation%20lit%20a%20fire%20in%20me.%20My%20job%20was%20comfortable%2C%20but%20I%20missed%20the%20adrenaline%20of%20pushing%20boundaries%20and%20overcoming%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20my%20role%20at%20W%26amp%3BD%2C%20which%20had%20shifted%20from%20creating%20to%20maintaining.%20Building%20new%20systems%20and%20implementing%20fresh%20ideas%20were%20the%20activities%20that%20fueled%20my%20passion.%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20challenged%2C%20and%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20didn't%20offer%20that%20kind%20of%20growth.%20Managing%20a%20bigger%20team%20or%20getting%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%26quot%3B%20title%20was%20less%20appealing%20than%20the%20chance%20to%20learn%20and%20innovate%20in%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there%20was%20AI.%20It%20was%20starting%20to%20sweep%20across%20industries%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20bystander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeciding%20to%20leave%20my%20VP%20role%20was%20scary%20but%20the%20fear%20of%20complacency%20and%20the%20prospect%20of%20looking%20back%20with%20regret%20for%20not%20pursuing%20my%20passions%20were%20far%20greater%20motivators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20challenge%20myself%20to%20grow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20away%20from%20a%20role%20that%20may%20seem%20perfectly%20set%20up%20for%20you%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20feels%20like%20golden%20handcuffs%2C%20requires%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20what%20you%20value%20most.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20was%20about%20continual%20growth%20and%20not%20wanting%20to%20get%20left%20behind%20as%20the%20pace%20of%20engineering%2C%20especially%20in%20AI%2C%20began%20to%20accelerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20shy%20away%20from%20the%20discomfort%20of%20leaving%20security%20behind.%20In%20that%20discomfort%2C%20you'll%20find%20the%20most%20significant%20opportunities%20for%20growth%20and%20innovation.%20Trust%20in%20your%20ability%20to%20navigate%20the%20unknown%2C%20and%20remember%20that%20the%20skills%20and%20resilience%20you%20build%20through%20this%20process%20are%20invaluable%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20earning%20less%20than%20I%20was%20before%2C%20but%20that's%20because%20we're%20reinvesting%20all%20profits%20back%20into%20the%20business.%20We're%20very%20proud%20to%20be%20bootstrapped%20yet%20profitable%20and%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20learned%20a%20lot%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20plenty%20of%20mistakes%20in%20my%20career%2C%20but%20my%20most%20recent%20one%20was%20in%20January%20when%20I%20built%20a%20system%20and%20unexpectedly%20racked%20up%20over%20%245%2C000%20in%20computing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20resolved%20after%20editing%20a%20few%20lines%20of%20code%2C%20but%20it%20showed%20me%20just%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20forecast%20what%20a%20new%20system%20will%20cost%20before%20deploying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20distill%20one%20piece%20of%20concrete%20advice%20for%20people%20itching%20to%20leave%20their%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20it%20would%20be%20this%3A%20embrace%20the%20challenge%20of%20leaving%20a%20comfortable%20position%20not%20as%20a%20loss%2C%20but%20as%20a%20critical%20step%20toward%20personal%20and%20professional%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-vp-role-age-25-build-startup-dont-regret-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714467902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fdfa610dfcda409649751%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-vp-role-age-25-build-startup-dont-regret-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Timothy%20Gamble%20left%20his%20role%20as%20the%20VP%20of%20data%20engineering%20at%20Walker%20%26amp%3B%20Dunlop%20to%20cofound%20an%20AI%20startup%20in%20the%20real-estate%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Perri%20Ormont%20Blumberg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-vp-role-age-25-build-startup-dont-regret-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Polls%3A%20YSRCP%2C%20TDP%2C%20Congress%20Face%20A%20Momentous%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flsocc93g_andhra_625x300_30_April_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%5C%22%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20underway%20to%20elect%20a%20government%20simultaneously%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20State%2C%20offers%20an%20exciting%20opportunity%20to%20political%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20analyse%20the%20elections%20is%20by%20considering%20how%20much%20recall%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20incumbent%20government%2C%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjagan-mohan-reddy%5C%22%3EChief%20Minister%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%3C%2Fa%3E%20YSR%20Congress%20party%2C%20will%20get%20among%20voters%20as%20they%20cast%20their%20vote%20on%20May%2013%20on%20two%20separate%20ballots.%20The%20ultimate%20result%20could%20either%20extend%20the%20faith%20in%20the%20party%20for%20five%20more%20years%20or%20entrust%20the%20reins%20to%20another%20player%2C%20while%20also%20handing%20down%20a%20similar%20verdict%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Findia-decides%2Fjaganmohan-reddy-is-a-habitual-liar-alleges-chandrababu-naidu-778643%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BJaganmohan%20Reddy%20Is%20A%20Habitual%20Liar%2C%26quot%3B%20Alleges%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20possibility%20could%20be%20that%20when%20the%20votes%20are%20counted%20on%20June%204%2C%20results%20will%20showcase%20the%20electorate's%20innate%20ability%20to%20make%20a%20discerning%20choice.%20They%20may%20elect%20one%20party%20to%20rule%20the%20state%2C%20and%20another%20to%20handle%20the%20national%20affairs.%20A%20number%20of%20instances%20can%20be%20cited%20to%20validate%20both%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistorical%20Trend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20pitched%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Reddy%20and%20his%20YSR%20Congress%20party%20is%20the%20formidable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fit-will-be-a-sweep-says-chandrababu-naidu-as-his-party-ally-jana-sena-finalise-alliance-with-bjp-5206566%5C%22%3ETelugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)-Jana%20Sena%20(JS)-Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20combine%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20one%20side%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20latter's%20presence%20is%20bolstered%20by%20Y.S.%20Sharmila%2C%20the%20estranged%20sister%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh's%20political%20landscape%20underwent%20a%20major%20transformation%20four%20decades%20ago.%20The%20TDP%2C%20a%20regional%20outfit%20founded%20by%20Nandamuri%20Taraka%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20established%20itself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20players%20in%20the%20state.%20For%20years%20following%20that%2C%20Andhra%20voters%20largely%20backed%20the%20same%20party%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20Parliament%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagan-mohan-reddy-is-not-ys-rajasekhar-reddys-successor-says-sister-ys-sharmila-5398602%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20Is%20Not%20YS%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy's%20Successor%2C%20Says%20Sister%20YS%20Sharmila%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20carried%20on%20through%20the%20last%20decade%20when%20another%20regional%20player%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20entered%20the%20scene.%20Before%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20bifurcation%20in%202014%2C%20the%20state%20used%20to%20vote%20as%20one%20for%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20TDP%20won%2016%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20undivided%20state%20in%202014%2C%20while%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20bagged%20nine.%20The%20assembly%20elections%20were%20also%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20TDP%2C%20led%20by%20Nara%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20In%20the%20next%20elections%20in%202019%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20bagged%20151%20of%20the%20175%20assembly%20seats%20and%2022%20out%20of%20the%20total%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20the%20verdict%20be%20different%20now%3F%20As%20in%20every%20election%2C%20various%20factors%20are%20at%20play.%20Reddy%20is%20confident%20that%20people%20will%20vote%20him%20back%20into%20office%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20his%20government's%20welfare%20schemes.%20But%20the%20burden%20of%20incumbency%2C%20the%20charge%20of%20being%20inaccessible%2C%20and%20the%20cases%20pending%20against%20him%20can%20pose%20challenges.%20He%20is%20also%20facing%20heat%20from%20sister%20Sharmila%2C%20who%20now%20heads%20the%20state%20Congress%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20these%20conditions%2C%20a%20possible%20vote%20split%20driven%20by%20those%20who%20are%20loyal%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20to%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Sharmila's%20father%20Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20may%20end%20up%20helping%20the%20TDP-led%20alliance%20consolidate%20its%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20dominant%20Kamma%20community%2C%20now%20also%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20influential%20Kapus%2C%20with%20actor-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20of%20the%20JS%20positioning%20himself%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20this%20group.%20The%20actor%20is%20the%20brother%20of%20former%20Congress%20Union%20Minister%20and%20erstwhile%20superstar%20Chiranjeevi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Do-Or-Die%20Battle%20For%20Naidu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%2C%20who%20turned%2074%20this%20April%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20assembly%20election%20this%20year%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20political%20survival%3B%20it's%20more%20crucial%20than%20ever%20to%20re-establish%20the%20TDP's%20dominance%20and%20move%20forward%20on%20the%20succession%20plan%20with%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh.%20Having%20earned%20the%20reputation%20of%20an%20able%20administrator%2C%20Naidu%20is%20past%20his%20prime.%20The%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20voted%20for%20him%20in%202014%20hoping%20the%20person%20who%20developed%20the%20state%20and%20developed%20'Cyberabad'%20as%20an%20enviable%20IT%20capital%20would%20be%20the%20right%20person%20