%20to%20blackmail%20them%20into%20continuing%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714464720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fb41kcf4s_prajwal-revanna_625x300_19_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-prajwal-revanna-suspended-from-jds-over-sex-scandal-row-5555205%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20was%20today%20suspended%20from%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20or%20JD(S)%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20explicit%20videos%20-%20allegedly%20showing%20him%20sexually%20assaulting%20multiple%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-prajwal-revanna-suspended-from-jds-over-sex-scandal-row-5555205%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-prajwal-revanna-suspended-from-jds-over-sex-scandal-row-5555205%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-prajwal-revanna-suspended-from-jds-over-sex-scandal-row-5555205%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Columbia%20protesters%20take%20over%20academic%20building%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714464626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10F08%2Fproduction%2F_133248396_columbia23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68923528%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pro-Palestinian%20groups%20are%20occupying%20Hamilton%20Hall%20after%20defying%20a%20deadline%20to%20take%20down%20an%20encampment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A166%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68923528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68923528.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk