0shared%20that%20she%20wasn't%20comfortable%20referring%20to%20herself%20as%20middle-aged%20because%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20is%20middle%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20I%20hesitate%20at%20calling%20things%20'middle%20age'%20simply%20because%20I%20can%20be%20a%20semantic%20stickler%20and%20I%20could%20get%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20later%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHathaway%20first%20spoke%20about%20quitting%20alcohol%20during%20an%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fji12D_aObGw%3Fsi%3DXKGJsPUm7tgyKaxL%26t%3D147%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Ellen%20DeGeneres%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20quit%20drinking%20back%20in%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20told%20DeGeneres.%20%26quot%3BFor%2018%20years.%20I'm%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-sober-stopped-drinking-start-family-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estop%20drinking%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20my%20son's%20living%20in%20my%20house%20because%20I%20don't%20totally%20love%20the%20way%20I%20do%20it%20and%20he's%20getting%20to%20the%20age%20where%20he%20really%20needs%20me%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20clarified%20in%20an%20April%202019%20interview%20with%20Modern%20Luxury%20that%20she%20stopped%20drinking%20not%20because%20she%20had%20an%20alcohol%20problem%20but%20because%20she%20had%20really%20bad%20hangovers%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fparents%2Fanne-hathaway-not-drinking-while-son-is-young-hangovers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20last%20hangover%20lasted%20for%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20told%20Modern%20Luxury.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20at%20a%20stage%20in%20my%20life%20where%20there%20is%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20