https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-successful-tech-cofounders-couples-therapy-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecofounders%20are%20also%20going%20to%20couples%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcofounderclarity.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Matthew%20Jones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist%20who%20started%20focusing%20on%20cofounder%20coaching%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20clients%20are%20often%20drawn%20to%20therapy%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20psychological%20complexity%20of%20going%20through%20a%20high-stress%2C%20high-pressure%20situation%20with%20someone%20close%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20managing%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Matthew%20Jones%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fdd71ec0c696569fed89c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Matthew%20Jones.%3Cp%3EDr.%20Matthew%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Jones'%20clients%20work%20in%20tech%20and%20often%20deal%20with%20fast-paced%20work%20environments%20and%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20creates%20a%20bond%20that%20can%20either%20be%20leveraged%20to%20greater%20resilience%2C%20more%20closeness%2C%20better%20decision%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20Or%2C%20it%20can%20have%20the%20opposite%20effect%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bthe%20relationship%20actually%20starts%20to%20deteriorate%20your%20mental%20health%20and%20impact%20business%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20shared%20six%20of%20the%20biggest%20communication%20mistakes%20he's%20seen%20business%20leaders%20and%20cofounders%20make%20%E2%80%94%20from%20how%20they%20address%20conflict%20to%20ignoring%20it%20until%20it's%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20They%20only%20understand%20business%20language%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20there%20are%20three%20types%20of%20languages%20that%20all%20business%20teams%20speak%3A%20operational%2C%20psychological%2C%20and%20archetypal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOperational%20language%20is%20the%20one%20%26quot%3Bmost%20teams%20do%20relatively%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-email-lacks-emotional-intelligence-is-bad-for-business-psychologists-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrictly%20tied%20to%20work%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Comparatively%2C%20he%20said%20psychological%20language%20is%20slower.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20deliberate%2C%20more%20resource-intensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20requires%20a%20different%20approach%20for%20listening.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20he%20said%20archetypal%20language%20is%20more%20about%20your%20overall%20vibe%20around%20each%20other%2C%20such%20as%20walking%20on%20eggshells%20with%20the%20other%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20miscommunications%20around%20these%20two%20languages%20cause%20most%20of%20the%20problems%20his%20clients%20come%20in%20for%20because%20they%20influence%20how%20leaders%20navigate%20conflict%20and%20give%20feedback.%20Being%20able%20to%20speak%20all%20three%20languages%20is%20an%20important%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-accountant-soft-skills-freelancer-entrepreneur-delhi-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoft%20skill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20sign%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-lasso-emotional-intelligence-humility-leadership-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemotional%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20They%20don't%20check%20in%20enough%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20that%20when%20business%20leaders%20don't%20normalize%20listening%20and%20giv