%20Pet%2C%20Canada%20Pooch%2C%20Pepper%20Pet%2C%20Wildebeest%2C%20and%20Teckelclub%20coats%2C%20which%20Insider%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20dry%20weather%20and%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20restrictions%2C%20I%20could%20not%20test%20these%20jackets%20on%20dogs%20of%20multiple%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20in%20real%20rainy%20weather.%20Instead%2C%20I%20came%20up%20with%20a%20few%20tests%20to%20simulate%20rainy%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20verified%20the%20measurements%20of%20each%20by%20assessing%20their%20length%20from%20shoulder%20to%20tail%20and%20their%20girth%2C%20the%20width%20of%20the%20jacket%20at%20the%20chest's%20widest%20point.%20I%20took%20note%20of%20any%20jackets%20that%20differed%20from%20their%20advertised%20size%20or%20appeared%20to%20fit%20more%20tightly%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoak%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20soak%20test%20illustrated%20how%20each%20raincoat%20would%20stand%20up%20under%20heavy%20rain.%20Using%20leftover%20two-by-fours%2C%20we%20constructed%20a%20wooden%20dog%20with%20a%20belly%2013%20inches%20off%20the%20ground%20and%20a%20length%20of%2020%20inches.%20When%20Woody%20was%20ready%2C%20I%20wrapped%20a%20dry%20towel%20around%20its%20belly%20and%20dressed%20it%20in%20each%20jacket.%20I%20sprinkled%20the%20dog%20and%20raincoat%20with%20water%20from%20a%20hose%20for%20two%20minutes%2C%20then%20carefully%20removed%20the%20jacket%20to%20look%20for%20any%20spots%20where%20the%20water%20had%20seeped%20through.%20I%20also%20checked%20the%20interior%20lining%20of%20the%20jacket%20to%20see%20if%20moisture%20had%20penetrated%20without%20wetting%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20cleaning%20test%20had%20three%20parts.%20First%2C%20I%20wiped%20a%20handful%20of%20mud%20on%20the%20exterior%20of%20each%20jacket%20and%20let%20it%20dry%20overnight.%20Next%2C%20I%20attempted%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20mud%20using%20a%20