ived%20in%20a%20small%20home.%20My%20father%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278952%2Fkerala-gardener-grows-135-fruit-trees-in-plastic-drums-on-terrace-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20backyard%20and%20we%20helped%20him%20in%20gardening.%20We%20would%20be%20very%20excited%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20the%20well%20and%20water%20all%20the%20plants%20together.%20He%20would%20teach%20us%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20plants.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20be%20in%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20piqued%20her%20interest%20in%20gardening%20and%20her%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20her%20own.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20would%20not%20grow%20flowering%20plants.%20But%20I%20always%20desired%20to%20grow%20roses%20and%20%3Cem%3Erajanigandha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tuberose).%20So%2C%20when%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20set%20up%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20roses%20and%20other%20flowers.%20My%20father%20would%20bring%20guests%20to%20my%20garden%20and%20proudly%20say%20that%20this%20was%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayanti%20grows%20fruits%20like%20guavas%2C%20pomegranates%2C%20oranges%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20chikoos%20on%20her%20terrace.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347569%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJayanti%20grows%20fruits%20like%20guavas%2C%20pomegranates%2C%20oranges%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20chikoos%20on%20her%20terrace.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20when%20the%20BSc%20graduate%20got%20married%2C%20she%20took%20her%20gardening%20interest%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20home%20along%20with%20her%20clothes%20and%20jewellery!%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%E2%80%99s%20place%20did%20not%20have%20many%20plants%20except%20bananas%20and%20drumsticks.%20I%20started%20planting%20flowering%20plants%20like%20marigolds%20and%20bougainvillaea%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20Jayanti%20visited%20an%20offline%20exhibition%20where%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20grafting.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20trees%20like%20mangoes%2C%20oranges%2C%20and%20chikoos%20were%20grown%20in%20a%20pot!%20Before%20this%2C%20I%20had%20only%20seen%20these%20trees%20on%20large%20farms.%20Unlike%20them%2C%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338660%2Fhow-to-grow-fruits-on-terrace-gardening-tips-visakhapatnam-woman-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20trees%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20just%205%20to%208%20feet%20in%20height%2C%20but%20they%20were%20yielding%20fruits.%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20grow%20such%20fruit%20trees%20at%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%E2%80%99s%20quest%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20mini%20jungle%20on%20her%20terrace%20and%20in%20her%20house.%20Along%20with%20seasonal%20vegetables%20like%20brinjals%2C%20cucumber%2C%20okra%2C%20spinach%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20radish%2C%20and%20more%2C%20she%20cultivates%2017%20kinds%20of%20fruit%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20guavas%2C%20pomegranates%2C%20oranges%2C%20cherries%2C%20star%20fruit%2C%20white%20jamun%2C%20mulberries%2C%20apple%20bear%2C%20water%20apple%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20chikoos%20on%20her%20terrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%2C%20I%20grow%20flowers%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20vegetables%20in%20my%20house%20spread%20across%20a%20total%20area%20of%20about%201%2C500%20square%20feet%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302262%2Fpatna-couple-grow-fruit-trees-plants-organic-vegetables-on-terrace-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20and%20balconies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20article%2C%20Jayanti%20shares%20secret%20tips%20and%20techniques%20that%20have%20helped%20her%20to%20grow%20fruits%20in%20her%20rooftop%20garden%2C%20which%20can%20help%20you%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayanti%20grows%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20including%20chikoo%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20brinjals%20on%20her%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%