ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ffarm-3-1713965019-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ffarm-3-1713965019-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ffarm-3-1713965019-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348194%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20waste%20that%20is%20produced%20once%20the%20flowers%20are%20ready%20to%20be%20shipped%20is%20made%20into%20vermicompost.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrikanth%E2%80%99s%20customers%20range%20from%20wholesalers%2C%20retailers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274041%2Fnat-geo-india-series-on-benhail-antao-louise-remedios-goa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20planners%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20others%20spread%20all%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20study%20further%20as%20a%20young%20man%20but%20life%20seemed%20to%20have%20other%20plans.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20there%20was%20no%20planning.%20I%20was%20just%20following%20the%20path%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20worked%20hard%2C%20these%20are%20the%20only%20two%20things%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713967455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ffarm-1-1713964787.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20in%20a%20family%20of%20traditional%20farmers%2C%20Srikanth%20Bollapally%20lived%20in%20poverty%20as%20a%20child.%20He%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20route%20and%20started%20growing%20flowers.%20Today%2C%20with%20a%20farmland%20of%20over%2050%20ac