-surgeries-medals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-water%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20very%20popular%20sport%20in%20India%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20promoted.%20And%20to%20also%20bring%20this%20to%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20set%20an%20example%20by%20accomplishing%20this%20incredible%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20efforts%20will%20be%20successful%20when%20we%20see%20more%20young%20talent%20from%20India%20opting%20for%20swimming%20and%20representing%20the%20country%20at%20prestigious%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20undertake%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20swimmers%20received%20permissions%20from%20relevant%20authorities%20like%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20India%20(MEA)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20India%20(MoD)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20India%20(MoHFW)%3B%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20and%20other%20Government%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20fitness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20and%20getting%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20two%20Governments%2C%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20the%20two%20swimmers%20left%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20from%20Dhanushkodi%20on%2013%20April%2C%202024%2C%20by%20boat.%20The%20boat%20ride%20itself%20was%20challenging%20and%20led%20to%20severe%20motion%20sickness.%20They%20slept%20on%20the%20boat%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20aim%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%