nise%20or%20pronounce%20ingredients%20in%20a%20product%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20good%20for%20you.%20Buy%20the%20product%20in%20which%20you%20can%20understand%20the%20ingredient%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%20are%20listed%20in%20order%20of%20their%20weight%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20ingredient%20is%20the%20one%20that%20is%20present%20the%20most%20in%20the%20packet.%20So%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20buying%20biscuits%2C%20the%20first%20three%20ingredients%20usually%20will%20be%20maida%20(refined%20wheat%20flour)%2C%20palm%20oil%20and%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20items%20that%20have%20less%20than%20five%20ingredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTry%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20that%20have%20more%20than%20five%20ingredients.%20As%20the%20ingredient%20list%20increases%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20inversely%20proportional%20to%20the%20nutritional%20benefits.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGo%20For%20Homemade%2FNatural%20Food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20the%20healthiest%20foods%20are%20the%20ones%20without%20any%20labels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20unlimited%20access%20to%20resources%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20for%20our%20health%20is%20to%20stay%20updated%20and%20informed%20about%20what%20we%20consume.%20There%20are%20multiple%20ways%20for%20us%20to%20inculcate%20safe%20practices%20and%20avail%20homemade%20options%20as%20well.%20Having%20the%20knowledge%20of%20which%20ingredients%20work%20best%20for%20us%20and%20which%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20can%20definitely%20help%20us%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%