Bengaluru%20residents.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20garden%20city%20ordered%20a%20whopping%2029%20million%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20an%20average%20of%20122%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20per%20minute%20just%20during%20breakfast%20hours!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20sky-touching%20numbers%20make%20one%20think%20%E2%80%94%20how%20did%20this%20delicious%20dish%20come%20into%20existence%3F%20Well%2C%20we%20did%20some%20research%20and%20came%20across%20some%20amazing%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20intriguing%20story%20comes%20from%20Udupi%20when%20a%20cook%20fermented%20some%20rice%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20make%20alcohol.%20Failing%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20poured%20the%20fermented%20batter%20on%20a%20hot%20pan%20and%20voila%20%E2%80%94%20he%20accidentally%20gave%20the%20world%20its%20first%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20that%20the%20dish%20was%20concocted%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20first%20century.%20While%20others%20believe%20that%20the%20Chalukya%20King%20Someshvara%20III%20who%20ruled%20Karnataka%20around%201126%20CE%20jotted%20down%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291624%2Fmillets-help-in-weight-loss-delicious-recipes-health-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20recipe%20for%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eunder%20the%20name%20%3Cem%3Edosaka%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20his%20book%20%E2%80%98Manasollasa%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20origin%20story%20may%20be%2C%20the%20dish%20that%20was%20created%20centuries%20ago%20is%20loved%20across%20the%20world%20even%20today!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDid%20you%20find%20these%20theories%20interesting%3F%20Here%20is%20a%20short%20video%20that%20you%20can%20watch%3A%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3C